Hacktoberfest 2024 is an exciting month-long celebration of open-source contributions, running from October 1st to October 31st, 2024.
It's a fantastic opportunity to give back to the community, sharpen your coding skills, and meet like-minded people.
Participants are encouraged to make four pull/merge requests to any open-source project on GitHub or GitLab.
This year, the event is sponsored by DigitalOcean, Cloudflare, and Quira.
You can register anytime between September 23 and October 31.
